                    <div class="col">
                        <p>Just outside of the bustling vibe of New York City, Madison in New Jersey is a beautiful and charming small-town with a welcoming community. From theaters and museums to international restaurants and a thriving music scene, downtown Madison has all the entertainment that you need close by to enjoy life at Drew University.</p>
<p>A peaceful vibe and picturesque campus, you will feel inspired to study in this environment. Do you feel like expanding your travels? New York City is a train ride away, offering all the opportunities and entertainment that come with being in a thriving city. For more exciting tips about living in Madison, visit our <a href="https://www.intostudy.com/downloads/city-guides/us/Drew_City_Guide_2019-20.pdf">City Guide</a>.</p>

